Privacy Policy for HAYADARAN

Effective Date: June 1, 2024

Welcome to HAYADARAN! This Privacy Policy outlines the types of information we do and do not collect from users of our application and how we handle that information. Please read this policy carefully to understand our practices regarding your privacy.

1. Introduction

HAYADARAN is an application created by Gor Ohanyan, designed to provide users with links to free Armenian books. We prioritize your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information.

2. Information We Do Not Collect

We do not collect, store, or share any personal information about our users. Specifically:

We do not require you to register or provide any personal details to use the application.
We do not track your location.
We do not access your device's contacts, calendar, photos, or any other personal data.
3. Use of the Application

HAYADARAN simply provides links to free Armenian books. These links direct you to external websites where the books are hosted. We do not collect any data regarding your usage of these links.

4. External Links

Please note that HAYADARAN contains links to third-party websites. This Privacy Policy does not apply to those third-party websites. We encourage you to read the privacy policies of any third-party websites you visit.

5. Security

Although we do not collect personal information, we take the security of our application seriously. We implement measures to ensure that the application remains safe and secure for our users.

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted within the application, and the effective date will be updated accordingly. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your information.

7. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or the practices of HAYADARAN, please contact us at:

Email: ohangor@gmail.com

Thank you for using HAYADARAN!

Sincerely,
Gor Ohanyan
Creator of HAYADARAN
